    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      765.81,
      518.67,
      806.69
    ],
    "text": "Investigations were initiated by the Thirukkovil Police Station following information received on the evening of 23.05.2026 regarding the death of a person due to a wild elephant attack in the Wattamadu area within the Thirukkovil Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      821.25,
      507.34,
      834.53
    ],
    "text": "The deceased has been identified as a 63-year-old resident of the Nawakkadu area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      849.08,
      534.2,
      889.99
    ],
    "text": "Preliminary investigations have revealed that the victim was attacked by a wild elephant while cutting grass for cattle. The body has been placed at the Thirukkovil Hospital mortuary, while further investigations are being carried out by the Thirukkovil Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
