      131.27,
      499.81,
      162.89
    ],
    "text": "Suspect Arrested in Connection with Double Murder in Dikoya \u2013 Hatton Police Station",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      177.37,
      538.09,
      218.25
    ],
    "text": "The Hatton Police initiated investigations on the night of 21.05.2026 into the murder of a 75-year-old woman and an 85-year-old man who were allegedly attacked with a sharp weapon inside a house in the Dikoya area within the Hatton Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      232.69,
      534.39,
      259.77
    ],
    "text": "Accordingly, on 23.05.2026, a team of officers from the Hatton Police Station arrested a suspect linked to the incident in the Petraso area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      274.36,
      386.11,
      287.64
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is a 37-year-old resident of the Hali Ela area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.42,
      302.09,
      542.58,
      327.24
    ],
    "text": "During the arrest, a gold necklace, pendant, pair of earrings, and a gold bar were recovered from the suspect\u2019s possession. Further investigations are underway by the Hatton Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
